<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css'/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css"
          integrity="sha384-JcKb8q3iqJ61gNV9KGb8thSsNjpSL0n8PARn9HuZOnIxN0hoP+VmmDGMN5t9UJ0Z"
          crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-B4gt1jrGC7Jh4AgTPSdUtOBvfO8shuf57BaghqFfPlYxofvL8/KUEfYiJOMMV+rV"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>

<div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
    <h4 class="alert-heading">Bravo ! Tu as réussi !</h4>
    <hr>
    <p class="lead">On va maintenant te présenter 15 paires de mots à la suite.</p>
    <p class="lead">Essaye de retenir la traduction de tous les mots !</p>
    <p class="lead">Plus tard, on te donnera le mot Hongrois et
        tu devras écrire la traduction en français
    </p>

</div>

<form action="/tests/memorize" method="post">

    <input type="hidden" readonly class="form-control" id="question" name="question" value="<%= question %>">
    <input type="hidden" readonly class="form-control" id="answer" name="answer" value="<%= answer %>">
    <input type="hidden" class="form-control" id="test_definition_id" name="test_definition_id"
           value="<%= testDefinitionId %>">

    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Appuie sur cette touche pour commencer !</button>
</form>

</body>
</html>
